com.reactivecascade.util

Class AssertUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.reactivecascade.util.AssertUtil

  • public class AssertUtil
extends Object
    Runtime assertions to make contracts explicit and code self-documenting

    These assertions have no impact on performance in a production build as they are disabled. You can configure this in your AsyncBuilder.
